Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——Text——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.99,0:00:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,来到这座岛后已经有一段时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.12,0:00:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,仍然不见救援队的踪影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.13,0:00:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,看来会是场长期战  我想探索一下这座岛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.22,0:00:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.58,0:00:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,鱼场  水源  植物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,想找找比这里更好的露营地及漂流物等等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.73,0:00:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,姑且想做好秋天或冬天的预防
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,想到这么远去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.28,0:00:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在考虑到风险的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,希望能有一个人陪我去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.27,0:00:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.24,0:00:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.93,0:00:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不  一个人就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.85,0:00:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,也不能让一人留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.11,0:00:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  誉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.66,0:00:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我和睦  谁比较可靠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.44,0:00:44.78,Comment,,0,0,0,,是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.75,0:00:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是  如果搭档是无能的话  就无法依靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.66,0:00:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定会带值得依靠的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.95,0:00:46.37,Comment,,0,0,0,,不不  是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.37,0:00:47.94,Comment,,0,0,0,,不  睦就别争了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:49.26,Comment,,0,0,0,,不不  明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.69,0:00:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真拿你们没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.37,0:00:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,要我陪你去也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.44,0:00:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这份自信是哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:00:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  誉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你要选谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:06.43,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭圆_GBK\fs25\bord0.2\c&H454449&\3c&H64645A&\pos(892,620)}绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:06.18,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭圆_GBK\fs20\bord0.2\c&H454449&\3c&H64645A&\pos(262,586)}石刀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:05.81,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭圆_GBK\fs20\bord0.2\c&H454449&\3c&H64645A&\pos(245,110)}蚵岩螺干
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.09,0:02:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那么拜托你们留守了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.13,0:02:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.87,0:02:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,慢走…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.14,0:02:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,情绪好低落
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.59,0:02:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,光脚走在沙子上比较轻松呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,天气很热  尽量走在潮水打过的沙子上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.81,0:02:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是珊瑚菜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可以生吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.78,0:02:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是夏天  还留了点纤维在嘴里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.71,0:02:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但是有点清脆  还挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这是日本的植物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,全世界都有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,所以没办法知道这是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.55,0:02:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这边应该是在日本周边的岛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,漂流物的名称虽然有英文和中文
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但是日文是最多的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如果离日本近的话  就能游回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这是在开玩笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,小心湿滑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,誉  这里不是码头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不  好像废弃很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,或许会有居住的遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真想找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定这里有人在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.07,0:03:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但绝对不能勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.07,0:03:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就到这里  差不多要生火了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚要在这里露宿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,誉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会选择我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你的性格谨慎  又有灵活的对应能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为睦最适合野外求生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那还挺担心留守的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不适合野外求生的那两人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮的香菇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:31.87,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn腾祥嘉丽大圆GB18030\fsp10\fs45\bord2\c&H6620FA&\3c&HFAF1FE&\pos(640,420)\b0}毒蝇伞(有毒)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.32,0:04:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,烧起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好黑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.64,0:04:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不敢去尿尿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,信赖度是零呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.23,0:04:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,天…天色变暗了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.48,0:04:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,誉  挺担心她们的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,才…才不是担心她们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.41,0:04:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,只是有点在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在这边遇到  真是巧合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.77,0:05:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们稍微散个步…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你们出现的很不自然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,真拿你们没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就四人一起在这露宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,0:05:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  誉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你们空手来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我只带了两人份的蚵岩螺干
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我在做屋顶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,利用树枝之类的东西做出紧急避难所的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(684,658)}Fast Bivouac
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,叫作紧急露营
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,要记住  誉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是哪找来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.11,0:05:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才在附近发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是捕鱼用的渔网
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那边再拉紧一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,要睡在这上面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.48,0:06:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好…好挤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,可是睡在枯叶上会有很多虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不如给这座岛取个名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我们无法知道  不过应该是有名字的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,暂定的名字  暂定的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,叫「九条岛」怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,用自己的姓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉是推理小说中会出命案的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,取我们每个人的名字的一个字来命名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(612,658)}无视白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahomushi岛!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,紫音  明日香  快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒  是螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好像连蟹壳也能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:07:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,非常香  很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,吃完之后  就马上开始探索这附近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,探索?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这里有港口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,所以很有可能附近有人居住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在这座岛上?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,难道我们能获救吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定能获救  我们去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.19,0:07:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是这里  把整座都找一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们用扇形探索法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们四人从不同方向走1000步再折回原地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧  你能准确数到1000吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,小瞧我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,245
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,246
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,247
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,248
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那个  步伐大概是60厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,1000步大概是600米吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,255 256 257
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,293 294
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,295 296 297
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,29…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,快看!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,找到柚子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶家的田里有种着  所以很快就认出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,真怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.68,0:08:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,柚子主要是在日本种植的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是日本周边的小岛的可能性又变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我也这样觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,紫音还没有回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  希望她不是迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,大…大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,房…房子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到房子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.68,0:08:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是这个方向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,可能有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,首先要借用一下电话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.53,0:09:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这个确实是房子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这也太破烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定只是因为房主离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,请问有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么看都没有人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.23,0:09:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不  这是重大发现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,将近一半已经倒塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,要进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,房顶几乎没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,地板也坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,梁柱和墙壁都倾斜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,实在无法在这里居住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,至少…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.54,0:09:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,誉没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.57,0:09:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来吃柚子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬  皮拨不开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,皮也能吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好苦  酸死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不过姑且还能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,也让我吃吃看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是大发现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可别吓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,剪刀?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,而且还非常破旧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.41,0:10:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这已经是坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,而且锈迹还非常严重  很难使用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不  没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都想得到金属
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你们看它的形状
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,非常理想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,首先把连接处破坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:31.44,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs30\bord1.5\c&H4745FE&\3c&HEEDFF6&\pos(336.733,128.134)}木质把手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,看不出来吗  能用来做小刀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:35.44,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs30\bord1\c&H6064FB&\3c&HEEDFF6&\pos(470.066,156.934)}螺栓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,而且还能附上把手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:38.40,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs30\bord1\c&H5E63FF&\3c&HEEDFF6&\pos(471.133,134.534)}把螺栓磨平
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,只要钻些孔加上螺栓  就能随时使用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,看来她非常喜欢小刀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:39.27,Comment,,0,0,0,,总之非常理想  真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.22,0:10:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,摘太多也只会腐烂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,只拿几天的份  吃完再来摘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.34,0:10:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去岛中央的高处看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定附近会有陆地  我也想看看岛的全貌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都看不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.66,0:11:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,果然这里是海洋的正中心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.18,0:11:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,烟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,下一集  Case.8
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.42,0:12:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,发现乐土!?
